2009-05-03  ddennedy <ddennedy@d19143bc-622f-0410-bfdd-b5b2a6649095>

  * configure, src/albino/Makefile, src/humperdink/Makefile,
  src/miracle/Makefile, src/modules/avformat/Makefile,
